queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory=cse/network/* {{src}}
| json field=_raw "proto"
| json field=_raw "$['id.resp_p']" as dstPort
| json field=_raw "$['id.orig_h']" as src
| where !(dstPort=443 OR dstPort=80 OR dstPort=8080)
| concat(proto,"/",dstPort) as tp 
| count by tp 
| sort -_count
| limit 10

_sourceCategory=cse/network/* {{src}}
| json field=_raw "proto"
| json field=_raw "$['id.resp_p']" as dstPort
| json field=_raw "$['id.orig_h']" as src
| json field=_raw "$['id.resp_h']" as dst
| if(isPublicIP(dst), "External", "Internal") as direction
| count by direction
| sort -_count

_sourceCategory=cse/network/* {{src}}
| json field=_raw "proto"
| json field=_raw "$['id.orig_h']" as src
| json field=_raw "uid"
| json field=_raw "$['id.resp_h']" as dst
| json field=_raw "$['id.resp_p']" as dstPort
| json field=_raw "orig_bytes" as bytes_in
| json field=_raw "resp_bytes" as bytes_out
| concat(proto,"/",dstPort) as pr
| bytes_in + bytes_out as total_bytes
| sum(total_bytes) as Bytes, values(pr) as Service by src, dst, uid
| sort - Bytes 
| Bytes / 1024 / 1024 / 1024 as gb_bytes
| limit 10 
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code from geo://location on ip = dst
| fields - latitude, longitude, city, region 
| fields src, dst, Service, uid, country_name, Bytes, gb_bytes
